REACH NEW HEIGHTS
WE'LL HELP TAKE YOU FURTHER.






WE ARE HAWK CAPITAL
Hawk Capital Partners is a private equity firm that seeks to make control investments in businesses operating in the lower middle market. Working with in-place management teams or ownership groups, we collaboratively develop a long-term plan to capitalize on growth opportunities in those businesses or otherwise identify tangible ways to improve the businesses. Because we are investing on a long-term basis and do not have limited partners, we execute on the plan without the "noise" and pressure of having to realize a capital event. We focus on getting the process right and then afford the necessary time for our theses to unfold.



STRATEGIC FOCUS


We are focused on acquiring businesses with exceptional management teams and partnering with those teams to unlock value.





STRATEGIC GROWTH


At Hawk Capital, we seek to acquire businesses that have significant growth opportunities that can be harnessed through operational improvements, capturing market share through add-on acquisitions, leveraging technology (including Internet sales channels), improving efficiencies in the capital structure or otherwise.





STRATEGIC ADVANTAGE


We manage our own capital so there is no time horizon for us to exit an investment. Without limited partners, we can move quickly to make our investments and be patient over the long term to build the best businesses we can. At Hawk Capital, we have extensive track records managing businesses, in numerous industries through all economic cycles and creating extraordinary returns.








